1940;;Four Sons;;American;;Archie Mayo;;Don Ameche, Eugenie Leontovich, Mary Beth Hughes;;drama war;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Four_Sons_(1940_film);;When the Germans invade Czechoslovakia in 1939, the four sons of a Czecho-German family follow different paths: Czech patriot, Nazi supporter, artist in America, and heroic German soldier.